\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Damelin \'28Pty\'29 Ltd is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education institution\'2C and is accredited to offer various higher education programmes in different fields. \line \line The Diploma in Fashion Design and Retail Buying served at the AC meeting of 23 February 2011. It was recommended that the decision be deferred pending the appointment of a second evaluator\line \cell \pard 

